cat << EOF
CMU Flite (festival-lite) is a small, fast run-time open source text to speech
synthesis engine developed at CMU and primarily designed for small embedded
machines and/or large servers. Flite is designed as an alternative text to
speech synthesis engine to Festival for voices built using the FestVox suite of
voice building tools.
EOF

